        <h1>🏷️ Discount Calculator</h1>
        <p class="calc-intro">Calculate the final price after any discount and see exactly how much you save.</p>

        <div class="card">
          <label>Original price</label>
          <input type="number" id="disc-price" placeholder="89.99" oninput="calcDisc()">

          <label>Discount type</label>
          <select id="disc-tipo" onchange="toggleDiscType()">
            <option value="pct">Percentage off (%)</option>
            <option value="fixed">Fixed amount off</option>
          </select>

          <label id="disc-val-label">Discount (%)</label>
          <input type="number" id="disc-val" placeholder="20" oninput="calcDisc()">

          <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:0.5rem;margin-bottom:1rem">
            <button onclick="setDisc(5)" style="padding:0.35rem 0.75rem;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;background:var(--bg);cursor:pointer;font-size:0.825rem">5%</button>
            <button onclick="setDisc(10)" style="padding:0.35rem 0.75rem;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;background:var(--bg);cursor:pointer;font-size:0.825rem">10%</button>
            <button onclick="setDisc(15)" style="padding:0.35rem 0.75rem;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;background:var(--bg);cursor:pointer;font-size:0.825rem">15%</button>
            <button onclick="setDisc(20)" style="padding:0.35rem 0.75rem;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;background:var(--bg);cursor:pointer;font-size:0.825rem">20%</button>
            <button onclick="setDisc(25)" style="padding:0.35rem 0.75rem;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;background:var(--bg);cursor:pointer;font-size:0.825rem">25%</button>
            <button onclick="setDisc(30)" style="padding:0.35rem 0.75rem;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;background:var(--bg);cursor:pointer;font-size:0.825rem">30%</button>
            <button onclick="setDisc(50)" style="padding:0.35rem 0.75rem;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;background:var(--bg);cursor:pointer;font-size:0.825rem">50%</button>
            <button onclick="setDisc(70)" style="padding:0.35rem 0.75rem;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;background:var(--bg);cursor:pointer;font-size:0.825rem">70%</button>
          </div>

          <div class="result-box" id="disc-res">Enter the price and discount</div>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-top:2rem;padding-top:1.5rem;border-top:1px solid var(--border)">
          <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:1rem">How to calculate a discount</h2>
          <p style="color:var(--muted);font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1rem">To calculate a percentage discount manually, multiply the original price by the discount percentage and divide by 100 to get the savings amount. Then subtract that from the original price to get the final price. For example, 20% off £89.99 — savings = £89.99 × 20 / 100 = £18.00 — final price = £89.99 − £18.00 = £71.99.</p>
          <p style="color:var(--muted);font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.8">A quicker method is to multiply by (1 − discount/100). For 20% off: £89.99 × 0.80 = £71.99.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <aside class="calc-sidebar">
        <div class="card sidebar-card">
          <h2>What is a discount calculator?</h2>
          <p>A discount calculator helps you instantly find the final sale price after a percentage or fixed amount discount. It also shows you the exact savings so you can compare deals quickly while shopping.</p>
        </div>
